Package adqlParser.query.function

Class Summary
ADQLFunction Represents any kind of function.
Exists Represents the function EXISTS of SQL and ADQL.
InFunction It represents the In function of SQL and ADQL.
MathFunction It represents any basic mathematical function (complete list in MathFunctionType).
SQLFunction It represents any SQL function (COUNT, MAX, MIN, AVG, SUM, etc...).
UserFunction It represents unknown functions: they are thus considered as user functions.
